            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Device</div><span class="short tooltip-red" data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="Frequency Shift Keying">FSK</span>/<span class="short tooltip-red" data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="Facsimile">FAX</span> demodulator and antenna/receiver diversity unit            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Purpose</div>Decoding <span class="short tooltip-red" data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="High Frequency (3-30 MHz)">HF</span> teleprinter (telex) and facsimile (fax) signals            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Model</div>TG-1001M            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Manufacturer</div><a href="../../../manuf/teltron">Teltron</a>            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Reseller</div><a href="../../../manuf/hagenuk">Hagenuk</a>            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Year</div>1987 ~            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;"><span class="short tooltip-red" data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="National Stock Number (Nato Stock Number)">NSN</span></div>5820-12-310-9950            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Inputs</div>2 &#215; <span class="short tooltip-red" data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="Audio Frequency">AF</span>, 2 x <span class="short tooltip-red" data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="Intermedia Frequency">IF</span>, 2 x antenna            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Outputs</div>TTY, RS232/MIL188, Fax 2-tone, Fax grey-scale            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;"><span class="short tooltip-red" data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="Intermedia Frequency">IF</span></div>30 kHz            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Power</div>&bullet; Mains 230 V/<span class="short tooltip-red" data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="Alternating Current">AC</span> (22 W)<br /><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;"></div>&bullet; 24 V <span class="short tooltip-red" data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="Direct Current">DC</span> (18 W)            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Temperature</div>-10&#176;C to +55&#176;C            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Storage</div>-40&#176;C to +70&#176;C            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Humidity</div>95% &#64; +40&#176;C, non-condensing            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Dimensions</div>484 &#215; 435 &#215; 44.2 mm            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Weight</div>6212 g          </ul>
